                                                             SERVER CREATION

        Basic Commands
          
           1.Create package.json - npm init
           2.Create Nodemodules - 
               Install Express - npm i express


        Basic Steps

           1. create a folder -(BankServer)
           2. create a package.json file(npm init)
           3. create a Nodemodule file( npm express)
           4. create Index.js file
           5. import express insde index .json
           6. create app using express
           7.set up port number
           8.ressolving http request
           9. install nodemon - npm i -g nodemon
           10. http response code
               1xx -information
               2xx- succesfull
               3xx -redirection
               4xx -client error
               5xx -server error

            11. JWT Token - authentication 
               To check login or not ?

              login ------token generate------>client----- req to deposit to token ---->server token check ?

              Install JWT Token - jsonwebtoken

                npm i jsonwebtoken

                 to generete a new JWT Token - sign()


            12. Middleware - to verify the token 

               - it  comes in tgr middlee of the request and response 
               - it also provide access to many function 

                    1. Application level middleware
                      for entire application

                    2.Router - level - middleware 
                      - to verify token
                         to vlidate the token - verify()

            13.Database integration -
                  1)install mongoose - npm i mongoose (for connecting nodejs mongo1db)
                  2)DB connect via mongoose
                  3)create a model using mongoose

            14.Asynchronous function resolving
                  1)Resolving state -the()
                  3)Rejection state -catch()

            15.CORS -Cross origin resourse sharing
                   install cors -npm i cors
                   

        

